In the HBO documentary Thought Crimes Gilberto Valle talks about his 2012 arrest and claims that he plotted to kidnap, torture, and eat his wife and other women online . 
  The former New York City police officer was cleared of conspiring to abduct, cook and eat women in July . 
  He was convicted in 2012 but his conviction was thrown out in November . 
  In the film Valle says he has dark fantasies but never intended to hurt anyone . 
 